What is Spring Cloud Stream ?
is it a way to stream messages to and from any message queue / streaming - like kafka, Solace, AWS kinesis, SQS etc.
What is Spring Cloud Stream Binder ?
what is  Apache Kafka binder ?
what is diff. b/w spring-cloud-stream-binder-kafka and spring-cloud-starter-stream-kafka ? which one is latest ?

Overview:
The Apache Kafka Binder implementation maps each destination to an Apache Kafka topic. The consumer group maps directly to the same Apache Kafka concept.
Partitioning also maps directly to Apache Kafka partitions as well.

